Left Turn🛩️⤴️
-
Pressure on the seat, feeling the gravity of the motion, escaping the truth of beeing pulled back to the ground. The earth beneath becomes the surreal, beginning to tild up as you move into the turn. You transform into the plane you are sitting in. This feeling of lightness, not realizing the truth of the whole trick our mind plays with us. After you finished the turn you have either realized that reality is not always what it seams or you are just releaved to fly straight again.
Do you love or hate turns? 😔⤴️⤵️
#上海 #shanghai

Winter wonderland on the Great Wall at sunrise ❄️❄️❄️ Beijing just had its second snowfall and Xiao Wei (@greatwallmylove) and I were ready for it!
.
We drove to Jinshanling (which is both of our favorite sections of the wall!) and woke up early to catch the sunrise... and what a sunrise it was! Xiao Wei is an incredible photographer and captured the light and movement here wonderfully. I feel so lucky we were able to experience this magical and rare day on the Great Wall!
#thegreatwall #长城

Zhaoxing Dong Village, located in Liping County, southeast of Guizhou Province, is one of the largest Dong Villages in Qiandongnan area in Guizhou. Walking into Zhaoxing Dong Village, one will feel as though the clock is being turned back. Through the village, we can see hundreds of wooden-stilt houses built in a style of Chinese minority, which show another perspective of Chinese culture.
@_ik_wong
Thanks to my awesome Rachel for providing me such a perfect RAW.
